xpath

xpath is used to navigate through elements and attributes in an XML document.

*Terminology*
• Nodes:
  - element
  - attribute
  - text
  - namespace
  - comment
• Atomic values: nodes which there is no children or parent

*Relationship of nodes*
• Parents
• Children
• Sibling
• Ancestor
• Descendant

*Select node*
• Node names
• / root node
• . current node
• .. parent node
• @ attribute

*Wild card*
• matches any element node
• @* matches any attribute node
• node() matches any node of any kind
